How often does “repentance’” occur in the scriptures?

157 TIMES!

What books most often mention “repentance”?

What other words are used in verses with “repentance”?

† These are terms that highly correlate with “repentance”. They not only appear often, but they usually only appear in verses that contain “repentance”.
